ygData.messageBody:
Actually on Solusek Ro there was a gm event last nightthat has to do
with the DE. In West FP a mage summoned a skeleton for a pet then
dissapeared, and the pet promptly slew everything within the mage
guild(I watched as it happened). For a while it just stood there till a
high level paladin on our server slew it, and then the mage reappeared
again. He spoke of the Ilkath Zan, a DE society who was watching us with
their agents, about how they gave him that book in the form a human,
hoping he would cast its spell, that they were watching us as we spoke,
and that those who helped slay the skelton were doomed(yay for me).
After the undead battle we had fought(and considering all the deaths,
and how one mob escaped) we lost in sro past sunday I feel that there is
something brewing in those gms mind.

Talonus DuPrey
Wandering Minstrel of Solusek Ro
